Package org.powertac.common.repo

Repositories that need to exist in both the Power TAC simulation server and in brokers.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    DomainRepo
    DomainRepo types need to be recycled at pre-game time.
  • Class Summary

    BootstrapDataRepo
    Repository for data contained in a bootstrap record.

Package org.powertac.common.repo Description

Repositories that need to exist in both the Power TAC simulation server and in brokers. Most of them are populated as their target types are created or received as incoming messages.
